headline.print_headline: A Guide to Daily Developments in Iraq
headline.main: A Guide to Daily Developments in Iraq

lead_paragraph: The U.S. stepped up efforts to persuade Iraqi officials to stick to their official timetable of seating a new government soon in hopes that it can foster national reconciliation where previous efforts have failed in order to stem the rapidly expanding Sunni insurgency led by an al-Qaida breakaway group, the Islamic State of Iraq and the Levant.
